106	  both sides being equal to the genus $g(C)$. Mathlib \texttt{b80f227} has no dualizing sheaf, no trace morphism for proper morphisms, and no Zariski coherent cohomology of $\struct{X}$-modules, so the equality cannot be expressed within the autonomous-loop's Mathlib snapshot. Cross-reference: Hartshorne~III.7 and Stacks Tag~0FVU.
